{"id":283382,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/小妖uu-关于青春文学出版物的批示/","date":"2013-03-11T08:45:30Z","modified":"2013-03-11T08:45:30Z","title":"小妖UU | 关于青春文学出版物的批示","content":"<p>@小妖UU：今天一位编编朋友给我发了一个写文的注意事项，据说是上头的新规定，其中不能有高富帅白富美或早恋同性恋情节什么也就罢了，当我看到第八条时突然暗自庆幸自己写魔幻写的不多，因为：魔幻类作品要防止超能力、灵力、转世、重生、轮回、修仙等唯心概念……囧了吧！大家看看新政策，求破解！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/541f1af5jw1e2lotgg1lvj.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-283383\" alt=\"541f1af5jw1e2lotgg1lvj\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/541f1af5jw1e2lotgg1lvj.jpg\" width=\"438\" height=\"1026\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/541f1af5jw1e2lotgg1lvj.jpg 438w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/541f1af5jw1e2lotgg1lvj-128x300.jpg 128w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/541f1af5jw1e2lotgg1lvj-437x1024.jpg 437w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 438px) 100vw, 438px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18269,10466,20534],"tags":[9540,22346,9212]}